# 2.3 Stakeholder Needs

## Store Owner (Youssef Al-Ruqi)

### Responsibilities

- Define business goals.
- Monitor overall store performance.
- Review revenue reports.
- Monitor inventory performance.

### Needs

- Sales dashboards.
- Business reports.
- Revenue statistics.
- Product performance analysis.
- Inventory summaries.

### Main Goal

Increase online furniture sales while maintaining efficient inventory management and high customer satisfaction.

---

## Store Manager (Sarah Mansour)

### Responsibilities

- Manage furniture products.
- Manage categories.
- Update inventory.
- Process customer orders.

### Needs

- Fast product management interface.
- Product image management.
- Inventory monitoring.
- Low-stock alerts.
- Sales dashboard.

### Main Goal

Maintain an accurate product catalog and ensure efficient order fulfillment.

---

## Payment Officer (Ahmed Rayyan)

### Responsibilities

- Review payment submissions.
- Approve or reject payments.
- Maintain payment history.

### Needs

- Payment dashboard.
- Pending payment list.
- Payment history.
- Payment logs.
- Rejection reason tracking.

### Main Goal

Ensure every customer payment is accurately verified and recorded.

---

## Customer (Deema Khaled)

### Responsibilities

- Browse furniture products.
- Place orders.
- Track deliveries.
- Submit verified reviews.

### Needs

- Easy product browsing.
- Powerful search and filtering.
- Persistent shopping cart.
- Secure checkout.
- Order tracking.
- Address management.
- Responsive bilingual interface.

### Main Goal

Purchase furniture easily through a secure and user-friendly online shopping experience.

> **Note:** Wishlist is planned as a future enhancement and is not available in the current version.

---

## Administrator (Khaled Al-Najjar)

### Responsibilities

- Manage users.
- Assign roles.
- Moderate reviews.
- Review audit logs.

### Needs

- Role-Based Access Control (RBAC).
- Audit logging.
- User management.
- System monitoring.
- Security management.

### Main Goal

Maintain platform security, data integrity, and proper access control.

