# 2.5 User Roles Summary

The Ruqi Store system defines four application roles:

| Role | Description |
|---|---|
| **Customer** | Browse products, place orders, manage addresses, submit verified reviews |
| **Store Manager** | Manage products, inventory, categories, and order fulfillment |
| **Payment Officer** | Verify customer payments and maintain payment records |
| **Administrator** | Manage users, roles, audit logs, and review moderation |

All protected pages use ASP.NET Core Identity role-based authorization:

```csharp
[Authorize(Roles = "Customer")]
[Authorize(Roles = "StoreManager")]
[Authorize(Roles = "PaymentOfficer")]
[Authorize(Roles = "Admin")]
```

